# lab/dpo/.gitignore -- keep held-out / bait / runtime OUT of public git
# (pack v244 sec 3.0 DO-FIRST landmine: one `git add .` publishes these and
#  kills the measurement -- §3.2). Public git carries ONLY datable provenance +
#  reproducibility (data + scripts + gate.log + reports).

# held-out eval (poisons measurement if it enters a future pretrain)
o0_heldout_gen.jsonl
o0_heldout*.jsonl

# bait sets + manual bait verdicts
*bait*

# runtime tier state / curated view (rebuilt each run; NOT provenance -- pack sec 1)
o0_tier_state.json
o0_verdicts_curated.jsonl

# backups / caches / logs / local data
*.bak.*
__pycache__/
logs/
data/
eval/o0/v282_retrieve_audit*.jsonl
eval/o0/step6_falsifier_E*.json
reports/PREREG_*.md
